comments: O'Neale (UTA) and Poole (GSW) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Poole (GSW) firms up in his screening position in Ingles' (UTA) path and gives Ingles a step of distance to avoid the contact, which Poole absorbs.
Ingles (UTA) maintains verticality and absorbs the body contact that occurs as Poole (GSW) jumps forward toward him during his follow-through.
Ingles (UTA) brings his arm down during rebounding and marginal contact occurs with Looney's (GSW) left arm as Looney retrieves the ball.
Paschall (UTA) initiates contact across Looney's (GSW) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Wiggins (GSW) and Conley (UTA) engage and disengage with one another as they move around the screen.
Wiggins (GSW) and Conley (UTA) engage and disengage with one another as the defensive switch takes place following the pick.
Curry (GSW) and Conley (UTA) make incidental arm contact with one another after the ball becomes loose.
Curry (GSW) does not intentionally kick the ball after Conley (UTA) loses control of it.

Ingles (UTA) engages and disengages with Looney (GSW) as they jostle for rebounding position. Ingles and Looney each then make clean contact with the ball prior to any incidental arm contact occurring.
Porter Jr. (GSW) engages and disengages with O'Neale (UTA) as O'Neale moves to set the pick.
Porter Jr. (GSW) cleanly blocks Conley's (UTA) driving shot attempt prior to any incidental arm or body contact occurring.
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Curry (GSW) after the release and is jumping to the side of Curry when marginal body contact occurs.
Looney (GSW) and Paschall (UTA) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Curry (GSW) crosses half-court within eight seconds.
Conley (UTA) and Porter Jr. (GSW) engage and disengage with one another as the pick expires.
Bogdanovic (UTA) rests his hands on Wiggins' (GSW) back as Wiggins spins into the lane and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Poole (GSW) extends his leg to the side and initiates the marginal contact with Ingles (UTA), who is in a legal guarding position.
Porter Jr. (GSW) legally contests Bogdanovic's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Looney (GSW) avoids making contact with the ball while it is in the cylinder around the rim.
Curry (GSW) avoids making contact with O'Neale's (UTA) left arm as O'Neale attempts the controlled put-back.
